</style><p>2022 年 2 月 24 日，Rushia Junha 取消了与经纪公司 Hololive Productions 的合同。因此，有人猜测，此人<em>可能故意将露西亚俊河的淫秽物品带到东京迪士尼海洋，目的是为了指责他。</em> </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="7gEkdD8KgP"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/uruha-rushia-was-fired-by-cover-corp-due-to-credit-loss-such-as-breach-of-contract-and-false-declaration/">Junba Rushia封面公司取消VTuber合同“收到违反合同和虚假声明等信誉损失”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Rushia Junba封面公司终止VTuber合同‘收到违反合同和虚假声明等信誉损失’” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/uruha-rushia-was-fired-by-cover-corp-due-to-credit-loss-such-as-breach-of-contract-and-false-declaration/embed/#?secret=oUffTF6zdu#?secret=7gEkdD8KgP" data-secret="7gEkdD8KgP" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="qCfWDcsBkM"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/mens-esthetic-salon-in-tokyo-suspected-of-using-images-of-former-hololive-vtuber-uruha-rushia-and-others-without-permission/">东京一家男士美容院涉嫌未经授权使用前 Holo Live VTuber Rushia Junba 等图像</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“东京一家男士美容院涉嫌未经授权使用前 Hololive VTuber Rushia Junba 等图像” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/mens-esthetic-salon-in-tokyo-suspected-of-using-images-of-former-hololive-vtuber-uruha-rushia-and-others-without-permission/embed/#?secret=t1m6Ybziui#?secret=qCfWDcsBkM" data-secret="qCfWDcsBkM" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="7kFf6tgAWj"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/criticism-of-person-who-brought-obscene-hug-pillow-of-former-vtuber-uruha-rushia-to-tokyo-disney-sea/">对将前VTuber“Uruha Rushia”的淫秽抱枕带到东京迪士尼海洋的人的批评</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“对将前VTuber“Uruha Rushia”的猥亵抱枕带到东京迪士尼海洋的人的批评” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/criticism-of-person-who-brought-obscene-hug-pillow-of-former-vtuber-uruha-rushia-to-tokyo-disney-sea/embed/#?secret=yxWnuWc1mz#?secret=7kFf6tgAWj" data-secret="7kFf6tgAWj" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息）</p><p></p><p></p>该帖子<a href="https://p2y.jp/criticism-of-person-who-brought-obscene-hug-pillow-of-former-vtuber-uruha-rushia-to-tokyo-disney-sea/">首次出现在 P2y.jp 上</a><a href="https://p2y.jp">。</a> ; https://p2y.jp/criticism-of-person-who-brought-obscene-hug-pillow-of-former-vtuber-uruha-rushia-to-to-to-kyo-disney-sea/feed/ 0 96303
